sourcesContent: import React from 'react'; import { useNavigate } from 'react-router-dom'; import { Container, Typography, Box, Paper, Grid, Button, IconButton, Divider, } from '@mui/material'; import { Add, Remove, Delete } from '@mui/icons-material'; // Mock cart data - in a real app, this would come from a state management system const cartItems = [ { id: 1, name: 'Immunity Booster', price: 5.99, quantity: 2, image: 'https://source.unsplash.com/100x100/?orange-juice', }, { id: 2, name: 'Green Detox', price: 6.99, quantity: 1, image: 'https://source.unsplash.com/100x100/?green-juice', }, ]; function Cart() { const navigate = useNavigate(); const subtotal = cartItems.reduce((acc, item) => acc + item.price * item.quantity, 0); const tax = subtotal * 0.1; // 10% tax const total = subtotal + tax; return ( Shopping Cart {cartItems.length === 0 ? ( Your cart is empty ) : ( {cartItems.map((item) => ( {item.name} ${item.price.toFixed(2)} each {item.quantity} ${(item.price * item.quantity).toFixed(2)} ))} Order Summary Subtotal ${subtotal.toFixed(2)} Tax (10%) ${tax.toFixed(2)} Total ${total.toFixed(2)} )} ); } export default Cart;
